app/console cms:page:create "This is SparkRebel!" "/about" "<h3 class=\"aboutDark\">SparkRebel is a collaborative fashion and shopping inspiration destination where products, blogs, pictures &amp; content are added, shared and discovered. Our community of members, brands and bloggers contribute interesting products and content. SparkRebel is about sparking your style imagination. With over 3,000+ brands and a million+ items on the site, members can find, share and click-thru to purchase items at all their favorite stores.</h3><h4>What can you do on SparkRebel?</h4><p>See it.&nbsp; Love it.&nbsp; Spark it.</p><p>Take products, photos, blogs, articles-or anything on the web and spark it on to SparkRebel.</p><p>Use your bookmarklet, URL entry or manual upload features on our Add page to contribute anything that inspires you and your style.&nbsp; We call these bits of inspiration &ldquo;sparks&rdquo;.</p><p><a href=\"http://SparkRebel.com/add\">Click here</a> to get the bookmarklet.</p><p>You can organize your sparks on collections based on a specific topic (DIY Fashion Ideas, Shoes I Love, Boho Style, etc).</p><h4>Discover on SparkRebel</h4><p>On SparkRebel, members add inspiration, but they also discover and share it.&nbsp; When you find a spark you love, hover over the photo and click the &ldquo;respark&rdquo; button.&nbsp; This allows you to save and re-post the spark to your own collection and share it with the community.&nbsp; Find something cool, interesting or unique?&nbsp; Comment on the spark.</p><h4>Explore on SparkRebel</h4><p>When members and brand add sparks, they post to topic-specific channels.&nbsp; Channels cover everything from Beauty to Accessories to Weddings to Fashion Disasters.&nbsp; When you visit a channel, you&rsquo;ll see a stream of sparks based on the channel topic.&nbsp; We call it a stream because it&rsquo;s like a river of fashion photos and products.</p><h4>Make Friends on SparkRebel</h4><p>SparkRebel allows you to follow specific members and brands, as well as specific collections from a member or brand.&nbsp; To follow a brand/member, just click their name anywhere on the site.&nbsp; You&rsquo;ll be taken to their profile page, where you can follow all their collections, or just a specific collection.</p><h4>Mission</h4><p>We are the go-to inspiration fashion community for women to add, share and discover exciting products and content they love.&nbsp; Spark your style.&nbsp; Inspire others.</p><h4>Want to join SparkRebel?</h4><p>Click here to request an invite to our closed beta.</p><h4>Where are the SparkRebel headquarters?</h4><p>86 Chambers Street, Suite 704, New York, NY 10007</p><h3>Team at SparkRebel</h3><ul class=\"aboutTeam\"><li><h3>Elad Baron (CEO)</h3><p>Has served as CEO of several successful digital enterprises. In 2006 he co-founded and served as the CEO of BitWine.com, an Internet marketplace for real time expert services. In 1998, Elad Baron co-founded network security firm Whale Communications (today part of Microsoft) and served as its CEO through 2005. Prior to founding Whale, Mr. Baron was a co-founder and served as CTO and then CEO of SoftLink, a market leader in secure file transfer solutions.</p></li><li><h3>Omer Yariv (CTO)</h3><p>Has been writing and designing software for over 15 years.</p></li><li><h3>Lindsay Anvik (Director of Marketing)</h3><p>Has been a creative strategist in fashion and entertainment for over 7 years. Lindsay is a 3rd generation entrepreneur. Before joining PlumWillow, she co-founded Spree, a shopping website. She holds a BA from Connecticut College in American Studies, with a focus on feminism and popular culture.</p></li><li><h3>Liat Tsarfati (Product Manager)</h3><p>Is a consumer internet product management professional with 5 years of experience in fashion industry online marketing and user experience/graphic design. But she's a fashionista at heart with a strong addiction to social media, mobile apps, and E-commerce. She earned a BBA in Marketing and Advertising Summa Cum Laude with a minor in Graphic Design from Baruch College.</p></li><li><h3>Charlie Federman (Chairman)</h3><p>Has over 30 years experience building, financing and advising technology companies. He is the former Chairman of Broadview International, a boutique investment banking firm and former Managing Director of BRM Capital, a venture capital firm.</p></li></ul>"

app/console cms:page:create "Terms of Service" "/terms" "<p>PlumWillow Inc DBA SparkRebel (&ldquo;SparkRebel&rdquo;, or , &ldquo;us&rdquo;, &ldquo;our&rdquo;, &ldquo;we&rdquo;) provides a tool for you to organize and share articles of clothing that you love (&ldquo;Items&rdquo;) through the SparkRebel website located at www.SparkRebel.com (the &ldquo;Site&rdquo;). These Terms of Service (&ldquo;Terms&rdquo;) govern your access and use of the Site. &ldquo;You&rdquo; or &ldquo;Your&rdquo; means an adult user of the Site, or as the parent or guardian of any minor whom you allow access the Site, and for whom you will be held strictly responsible.</p><p>Please read these Terms carefully. These Terms govern your access to and use of the Site. You must accept these Terms prior to using the Site. By using or visiting the Site (including all Content available through the Site), you signify your assent to both these Terms and our Privacy Policy, which is available at www.SparkRebel.com/privacy.&nbsp; Changes may be made to these Terms from time to time.&nbsp; Your continued use of the Site will be deemed acceptance to amended or updated terms.&nbsp; If you do not agree to any of these Terms, please do not use the Site.</p><h5>Use of Site</h5><p>SparkRebel allows you to access and use the Site subject to the terms and conditions of these Terms for your personal use only. This does not allow you to make any commercial use or any derivative use of the Site, including any of its individual elements or Content (as defined below). You acknowledge that SparkRebel may, in its sole discretion and at any time, discontinue providing any part of the Site without notice.</p><p>Use of and access to the Site is void where prohibited. By using the Site, you represent and warrant that (a) all registration information you submit is truthful and accurate; (b) you will maintain the accuracy of such information; (c) you are 18 years of age or older or else, have your parent's or guardian's permission to enter into this agreement, or otherwise have the ability to form a binding contract; and (d) your use of the Site does not violate any applicable law or regulation or any obligation you may have to a third party.</p><p>You are welcome to link to the Site from your website, provided that your website does not imply any endorsement by or association with SparkRebel.</p><h5>Account Registration</h5><p>When you complete the registration process, you create a SparkRebel account. Your account allows you to access certain services provided by the Site, subject to the Terms and our Privacy Policy. SparkRebel reserves the right to refuse to allow a user to open an account for any reason, or to limit the number of accounts a user can establish on the Site, all at SparkRebel&rsquo;s sole discretion.</p><p>To create an account, you must select a username and password. You may not select a username that is used by someone else, and your username cannot be indecent, or otherwise offensive, or be used in any way that violates the Terms and common practices. You may not provide false information during the registration process.</p><p>You should not reveal your password to other users. SparkRebel will not ask you to reveal your password. If you forget your password, you can request to have a new password sent to your registered e-mail address. Your account is at risk if you let someone use it inappropriately and your account is subject to termination if you or anyone using your account violates SparkRebel Terms. If your account is terminated, you may not join SparkRebel again without express permission.</p><p>You agree to immediately notify SparkRebel of any unauthorized use of your account or password. You are fully and solely responsible for the security of your computer system and all activity on your account, even if such activities were not committed by you. SparkRebel will not be liable for any losses or damage arising from unauthorized use of your account or password, and you agree to indemnify and hold SparkRebel harmless for any improper or illegal use of your account, including any mail sent and any charges and taxes incurred, unless you have notified us via e-mail to support@plumwillow.com. that your account has been compromised, and have requested us to block access to it. This includes illegal or improper use by someone to whom you have given permission to use your account. We do not police for, and cannot guarantee that we will learn of or prevent, any inappropriate use of the Site.</p><h5>Termination of Account</h5><p>You agree that SparkRebel may for any reason, in its sole discretion and without notice, terminate your account, and remove from the Site any Content associated with your account. Grounds for such termination may include (i) extended periods of inactivity, (ii) violation of the letter or spirit of these Terms, (iii) fraudulent, harassing or abusive behavior, or (iv) behavior that is harmful to other users, third parties, or the business interests of SparkRebel.</p><p>If SparkRebel believes, in its sole discretion, that a violation of these Terms or any illegal or inappropriate behavior has occurred, we may take any other corrective action we deem appropriate. We reserve the right to investigate suspected violations of these Terms or illegal and inappropriate behavior on the Site. We will fully cooperate with any law enforcement authorities or court order requesting or directing us to disclose the identity, Content and behavior of anyone believed to have violated these Terms or to have engaged in illegal behavior on the Site. You may request termination of your SparkRebel account at any time and for any reason by sending an email to support@plumwillow.com Any suspension, termination, or cancellation shall not affect your obligations to SparkRebel under these Terms (including but not limited to ownership, indemnification, and limitation of liability), which by their sense and context are intended to survive such suspension, termination, or cancellation.</p><h5>Content</h5><p>Certain types of content may be made available through the Site. &ldquo;Content&rdquo; as used in these Terms means, collectively, all content on or made available on the Site, including but not limited to pictures of Items and text posted anywhere on the Site, whether by us or by any other member of user of the Site.</p><p>SparkRebel may allow you to post Content to the Site, including pictures of Items. You are fully and solely responsible for any Content you submit or post to the Site, and represent and warrant that such Content (a) complies with all applicable law and does not infringe third party intellectual property rights, including moral rights and privacy rights, (b) does not contain any defamatory, libelous, vulgar, obscene or otherwise offensive content, and (c) complies with applicable law. SparkRebel has no obligation to accept, display, review or maintain any Content. Moreover, SparkRebel reserves the rights to remove and permanently delete any Content, including any statements of any user, without notice and for any reason. Any posted or submitted Content shall not be considered confidential and may be disseminated by SparkRebel without any compensation to you. Items and Content you use or available through your account may be available to the public, and you should have no expectation of privacy in the same. This provision shall not apply to personal information that is subject to SparkRebel&rsquo;s Privacy Policy except to the extent that you make such personal information publicly available on or through the Site or in any Content. SparkRebel DOES NOT ENDORSE ANY CONTENT OR ANY OPINION, RECOMMENDATION, OR ADVICE EXPRESSED THEREIN, AND SparkRebel EXPRESSLY DISCLAIMS ANY AND ALL LIABILITY IN CONNECTION WITH CONTENT.</p><p>SparkRebel may choose at its sole discretion to monitor Content for inappropriate or illegal behavior, including through automatic means; provided, however, that SparkRebel reserves the right to treat user Content as content stored at the direction of users for which SparkRebel will not exercise editorial control except when violations are directly brought to SparkRebel&rsquo;s attention. SparkRebel has the right to edit, delete, distort or move user Content from the Site without notice for any reason at any time. Additionally, SparkRebel has the right to refuse to transmit, post or broadcast any user Content without notice for any reason at any time.</p><p>Content on the Site may contain descriptions of Items or other products, including for commercial sale. SparkRebel attempts to be as accurate as possible. HOWEVER, SparkRebel DOES NOT WARRANT THAT ANY ITEM OR PRODUCT DESCRIPTION IS ACCURATE, COMPLETE, RELIABLE, CURRENT, OR ERROR-FREE. We reserve the right to correct any errors, inaccuracies or omissions and to change or update Item or Content information at any time without prior notice (including after you have submitted an order).</p><p>Content on the Site comes from a variety of sources.&nbsp; You understand that SparkRebel is not responsible for the accuracy, usefulness, safety, appropriateness or intellectual property rights of or relating to this Content.&nbsp; Although users must agree to these Terms, it is possible that other users (including unauthorized users) may post or transmit offensive or obscene materials that you may be involuntarily exposed to such offensive or obscene materials, and you hereby agree to wave, and do waive, any legal or equitable rights or remedies you have or may have against SparkRebel with respect to thereto. It also is possible for others to obtain personal information about you due to your use of the Service, including any Content that you may choose to make available. Anyone receiving or viewing Content may use your information for purposes other than what you intended. We are not responsible for the use of any personal information that you disclose on the Service or through any Content. Please carefully select the type of information that you post on the Service or release to others. WE DISCLAIM ALL LIABILITY, REGARDLESS OF THE FORM OF ACTION, FOR THE ACTS OR OMISSIONS OF OTHER MEMBERS OR USERS (INCLUDING UNAUTHORIZED USERS), WHETHER SUCH ACTS OR OMISSIONS OCCUR DURING THE USE OF THE SERVICE OR OTHERWISE.</p><h5>Intellectual Property</h5><p>SparkRebel and its licensors own the Site, including all worldwide intellectual property rights in the Site, Content (except for Content posted by users), and the trademarks, service marks, and logos contained therein.&nbsp; Except as expressly permitted herein, you may not copy, further develop, reproduce, republish, modify, alter download, post, broadcast, transmit or otherwise use the Site or Content.&nbsp; You will not remove, alter or conceal any copyright, trademark, service mark or other proprietary rights notices incorporated in the Site or Content. All trademarks are trademarks or registered trademarks of their respective owners. Nothing in these Terms grants you any right to use any trademark, service mark, logo, or trade name of SparkRebel or any third party.</p><p>By submitting or posting any Items or Content, you grant SparkRebel and its successors and assigns a worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free, perpetual, sublicensable and transferable license to use, copy, distribute, transmit, modify, prepare derivative works of, publicly display, and publicly perform such Content on, through or in connection with the Site in any media formats and through any media channels, including without limitation, for commercially promoting the Site, as well as any Items or other commercially available items on the Site.</p><h5>Content Linked to by SparkRebel</h5><p>Portions of the Site (including, without limitation, advertisements) may involve linking to or using web sites belonging to third parties. The Site may also provide you with links to access the Sites of third party vendors or retailers including, without limitation, for the purpose of reviewing or purchasing Items. We have no control over third-party sites, and all use of third-party sites is at your own risk. Additionally, SparkRebel cannot accept responsibility for any payments processed or submitted through such third party sites, or for the privacy policies of any such sites. SparkRebel is not responsible for content or available by means of such sites. SparkRebel does not endorse any products or offered by third parties and we urge our users to exercise caution in using third-party sites.</p><h5>Content Restrictions</h5><p>Without limiting the foregoing, you agree that you will not transmit or post any Content that: (a) restricts or inhibits use of the Site; (b) solicits another person&rsquo;s password or other personal information under false pretenses; (c) impersonates another user or otherwise misrepresents yourself in any manner; (d) infringes (or results in the infringement of) SparkRebel&rsquo;s or any other third party&rsquo;s intellectual property or other rights; (e) is (or you reasonably believe or should reasonably believe to be) illegal, fraudulent, or unauthorized, or in furtherance of any illegal, counterfeiting, fraudulent, pirating, unauthorized, or violent activity, or that involves (or you reasonably believe or should reasonably believe to involve) any stolen, illegal, counterfeit, fraudulent, pirated, or unauthorized material; (f) does not comply with all applicable laws, rules, or regulations, including obtaining all necessary permits, licenses, registrations, etc. (in the case of any proposed or actual transaction, &ldquo;applicable&rdquo; refers to both your own location and to location(s) of all other parties to the transaction); or would cause SparkRebel to be in violation of any law or regulation, or to infringe any right of any third party; (g) contains falsehoods or misrepresentations that may damage SparkRebel or any third party; (h) imposes an unreasonably or disproportionately large load on our infrastructure; or (i) posts, stores, transmits, offers, or solicits anything that contains the following, or that you know contains links to the following or to locations that in turn contain links to the following: (i) material that we determine to be offensive (including material promoting or glorifying hate, violence, bigotry, or any entity (past or present) principally dedicated to such causes or items associated with such an entity), (ii) material that is racially or ethnically insensitive, material that is defamatory, harassing or threatening, (iii) pornography (including any obscene material, and anything depicting children in sexually suggestive situations whether or not depicting actual children) or may be harmful to a minor, (iv) any virus, worm, trojan horse, or other harmful or disruptive component or (v) anything that encourages conduct that would be considered a criminal offense, give rise to civil liability, violate any law or regulation or is otherwise inappropriate.</p><h5>Use Restrictions</h5><p>The software and technology underlying the Site is the property of SparkRebel, and you may not do or attempt to (a) decipher, decompile, disassemble, or reverse-engineer any of the software used to provide the Site; (b) frame or mirror any part of the Site; (c) circumvent, disable, or otherwise interfere with security-related features of the Site or features that prevent or restrict use or copying of any Content; (d) use the Site or Content in connection with any commercial endeavors in any manner, except for the purposes specifically set forth in these Terms; (e) use any robot, spider, site search or retrieval application, or any other manual or automatic device or process to retrieve, index, data-mine, or in any way reproduce or circumvent the navigational structure or presentation of the Site; (f) harvest, collect or mine information about other users of the Site; or (g) use or access another user&rsquo;s account or password without permission.</p><h5>Copyright Infringement</h5><p>SparkRebel will remove all infringing Content if properly notified that it infringes third party intellectual property rights, and may do so at its sole discretion, without prior notice to users at any time.</p><p>Under the Digital Millennium Copyright Act of 1998 (the &ldquo;DMCA&rdquo;), it is our policy to respond to copyright owners who believe material appearing on the Site infringes their rights. Users may need to obtain authorization of the owner of these materials for use of any other purpose other than viewing on the web.&nbsp; To obtain authorization, please contact the image owner as indicated on the source site, and not SparkRebel.&nbsp; SparkRebel is unable to give authorization to use copyrighted images.&nbsp; SparkRebel accepts no responsibility or liability for the content of any site included in any Content, or otherwise linked to by the, or for the user&rsquo;s use of such Content.&nbsp; We reserve the right to remove any Content without prior notice to you, any other user, or any third party.</p><p>If you believe that something appearing on the Site infringes your copyright, you may send us a notice requesting that it be removed, or access to it blocked. If you believe that such a notice has been wrongly filed against you, the DMCA lets you send us a counter-notice. Notices and counter-notices must meet the DMCA&rsquo;s requirements. We suggest that you consult your legal advisor before filing a notice or counter-notice. Be aware that there can be substantial penalties for false claims. Send notices and counter-notices to www.plumwillow.com/plum/contact. If you need to contact us for any other reason, please use our &ldquo;Contact Us&rdquo; section which is available at www.plumwillow.com/plum/contact.</p><h5>Disclaimers &amp; Disclaimer of Warranty</h5><p>Your use of the Site and Content is at your sole discretion and risk. The Site and Content are provided on an AS IS and AS AVAILABLE basis without