problems or traffic congestion on the Internet or on the Site, including any injury or damage to users or to any person's computer related to or resulting from participation or downloading materials in connection with the Site. Under no circumstances shall SparkRebel be responsible for any loss or damage, including personal injury or death, resulting from use of the Site, from any Content posted on or through the Site, or from the conduct of any Users of the Site, whether online or offline.</p><p>IN NO EVENT SHALL SparkRebel OR ANY OF ITS OFFICERS, DIRECTORS, EMPLOYEES, OR AGENTS BE LIABLE TO YOU FOR ANY DAMAGES WHATSOEVER, INCLUDING WITHOUT LIMITATION INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, PUNITIVE, OR CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES, ARISING OUT OF OR IN CONNECTION WITH YOUR USE OF THE SITE OR CONTENT, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO THE QUALITY, ACCURACY, OR UTILITY OF THE INFORMATION PROVIDED AS PART OF OR THROUGH THE SITE, WHETHER THE DAMAGES ARE FORESEEABLE AND WHETHER OR NOT SparkRebel HAS BEEN ADVISED OF THE POSSIBILITY OF SUCH DAMAGES. THE FOREGOING LIMITATION OF LIABILITY SHALL APPLY TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW IN THE APPLICABLE JURISDICTION AND IN NO EVENT SHALL SparkRebel'S CUMULATIVE LIABILITY TO YOU EXCEED AMOUNTS PAID TO SparkRebel FOR USE OF THE SITE. IF YOU HAVE NOT MADE ANY PAYMENTS TO SparkRebel FOR THE USE OF THE SITE, THEN SparkRebel SHALL NOT HAVE ANY LIABILITY TOWARDS YOU.</p><h5>Indemnification</h5><p>You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless SparkRebel and its respective employees, directors, officers, subcontractors and agents of each, against any and all claims, damages, or costs or expenses (including reasonable attorneys&rsquo; fees) that arise directly or indirectly from: (a) breach of these Terms by you or anyone using your computer or password; (b) any claim, loss or damage experienced from your use or attempted use of (or inability to use) the Site, including any transactions that you conduct or attempt; (c) your violation of any law or regulation; (d) your infringement of any right of any third party; and (e) any other matter for which you are responsible hereunder or under law. You agree that your use of the Site (including, without limitation, provision of services in connection with the Site) shall be in compliance with all applicable laws, regulations and guidelines.</p><h5>Miscellaneous</h5><p>These Terms shall be governed by the law of the State of New York exclusive of its choice of law rules, and without regard to the United Nations Convention on the International Sales of Goods. Your conduct may also be subject to other local, state, and national laws. Any action to be brought in connection with these Terms or the Site shall be brought exclusively in the state or federal courts in the State, City, and County of New York, United States of America, and you irrevocably consent to their jurisdiction. In any action to enforce this Agreement, the prevailing party will be entitled to costs and attorneys&rsquo; fees. Any cause of action against SparkRebel must be brought within one (1) year of the date such cause of action arose. In the event that any provision of these Terms is held to be unenforceable, such provision shall be replaced with an enforceable provision which most closely achieves the effect of the original provision, and the remaining terms of these Terms shall remain in full force and effect. Nothing in this Agreement creates any agency, employment, joint venture, or partnership relationship between you and SparkRebel or enables you to act on behalf of SparkRebel. Except as may be expressly stated in these Terms, these Terms constitute the entire agreement between SparkRebel and you pertaining to the subject matter hereof, and any and all other agreements existing between us relating thereto are hereby canceled.</p><p>We may at any time, without prior notice: (a) cancel any user account, or limit any user&rsquo;s access to all or portions of the Site; (b) change or eliminate any component of the Site; (c) impose, remove, or change any fees or charges for use of the Site or any feature thereof (including, without limitation, by changing the manner in which fees or time for sessions is calculated); and (d) assign any and all of our rights under these Terms to any other entity. These Terms will bind and inure to the benefit of each party&rsquo;s permitted successors and assigns. We may elect to keep archives of all or parts of the Site, but we cannot guarantee that anything available on the Site, or any records or information relating to the Site, will be archived, or that any archives will be preserved or made publicly available. We may delete any such information without notice, at our sole discretion.</p><p>Nothing contained in these terms shall be construed to limit the actions or remedies available to SparkRebel with respect to any prohibited activity or conduct. Non-enforcement of any term of these Terms does not constitute consent or waiver, and SparkRebel reserves the right to enforce such term at our sole discretion. No waiver of any breach or default hereunder shall be deemed to be a waiver of any preceding or subsequent breach or default. These Terms are for the benefit of SparkRebel (and respective assignees), and each shall have the right to assert and enforce its provisions against you directly on its own behalf. These Terms supersede any prior agreements between you and SparkRebel with regard to your use of the Site. We may assign our rights under these terms to any third party.</p>"

app/console cms:page:create "FAQ" "/faq" "<h3>What is SparkRebel?</h3><p>SparkRebel is a collaborative fashion and shopping inspiration destination where products, blogs, pictures and content can be added, shared and discovered.</p><h3>What is a Spark?</h3><p>A spark is any product, blog, picture or web content added to SparkRebel.&nbsp; Anything that inspires you can be a spark.&nbsp; Sparks can be added, shared and resparked.</p><h3>How do I add Sparks?</h3><p>Sparks can be added in three ways.&nbsp; You can use the bookmarklet by adding it to your browser toolbar and clicking it whenever you see something you want to spark.&nbsp; You can copy and paste the URL of where you want to spark an item from or you can upload a photo.</p><h3>How do I respark?</h3><p>When you find a spark that you love and you want to save it, hover over the image and click respark.&nbsp; Once you respark, you save your spark in a collection.&nbsp; Each collection shares sparks that have a similar topic.&nbsp; You can add your respark to a collection or create a new collection.</p><h3>What is a collection?</h3><p>A collection is where sparks of a certain topic are kept.&nbsp; When you respark a spark you like, it is saved in a collection.&nbsp; You can add it to a current collection you created or create a new collection.&nbsp; You can have as many collections as you want.</p><h3>How do I install the bookmarklet?</h3><p>To add the bookmarklet, just drag the &ldquo;Spark It!&rdquo; button to your bookmark toolbar.&nbsp; Make sure your settings have the bookmark toolbar showing so you can easily use it when you&rsquo;re sparking.</p><h3>How do I follow a member or a brand?</h3><p>Go to the member or brand&rsquo;s profile page and click &ldquo;follow member&rdquo; or &ldquo;follow brand&rdquo;.&nbsp; You can access a member and brand profile pages by clicking on their name anywhere on the site.&nbsp; When you follow a member or a brand you will see their sparks in your streams.&nbsp; You can also follow just a specific collection from the brand or member.</p><h3>How do I follow a collection?</h3><p>Click on the collection name anywhere on the site and then click &ldquo;follow collection&rdquo;.</p><h3>What are channels?</h3><p>Channels are streams of sparks that are devoted to a specific topic.&nbsp; When you view the celebrity and red carpet channel, the sparks will be of celebrity styles and red carpet photos.</p><h3>How do I get an invite?</h3><p>We&rsquo;re in private beta, so you need an invite to gain access to the site.&nbsp; When you first sign into the site, a pop up will appear and ask for an invite code.&nbsp; Below the invite code box you&rsquo;ll see &ldquo;request an invite&rdquo;.&nbsp; Click that link and we&rsquo;ll take you through the steps to get an invite.</p><h3>What is My Stream?</h3><p>My stream is the most recent sparks from collections you follow, as well as the sparks of your Facebook friends and members you follow.</p><h3>What is Brand Stream?</h3><p>Brand stream is a stream of sparks from brands you follow and have said you love.&nbsp; When you follow a brand, you&rsquo;ll see all of the sparks from their collections.&nbsp; You can also follow a specific collection from a brand, such as sale items or new products.</p><h3>The bookmarklet is not working, what do I do?</h3><p>Sometimes sites limit what types of content can be bookmarked from their site.&nbsp; In this case, it is a good idea to try to add the image via the URL on the Add page.&nbsp; If this doesn&rsquo;t work, you may not be able to spark the image.</p><h3>Why some of the images in the URL I entered not showing up on the Add page?</h3><p>Images have to be a certain size to be sparked. If it is less than a certain amount of pixels, it cannot be sparked.</p><h3>Why I don't see all the images on the page when I click on the bookmarklet?</h3><p>Images have to be a certain size to be sparked by the bookmarklet.&nbsp; If it is less than a certain amount of pixels, it cannot be sparked.</p><h3>How can I report a spark that has inappropriate content?</h3><p>You can flag a spark on the spark&rsquo;s page.&nbsp; If you see it in the stream, click the spark to go to the spark&rsquo;s page.&nbsp; There will be a &ldquo;flag this&rdquo; button on the spark&rsquo;s page.&nbsp; Click it and it will allow you to report the spark.</p><h3>How can I report a spark that is a copyright infringement?</h3><p>You can flag a spark on the spark&rsquo;s page.&nbsp; If you see it in the stream, click the spark to go to the spark&rsquo;s page.&nbsp; There will be a &ldquo;flag this&rdquo; button on the spark&rsquo;s page.&nbsp; Click it and it will allow you to report the spark and give details about copyright infringement.&nbsp; We will investigate the spark and take it off the site if there is infringement.&nbsp; We comply by the DCMA (Digital Media Copyright Act) and will honor any and all restrictions and requirements by this act.</p>"


app/console cms:page:create "Privacy and Security" "/privacy" "<p>PlumWillow Inc. DBA SparkRebel respects its users&rsquo; privacy. The following is our privacy policy.</p><p>PlumWillow has created this privacy statement (&ldquo;Statement&rdquo;) in order to demonstrate our commitment to customer privacy. The following discloses our information gathering and dissemination practices for the different functions and services available on this website. PlumWIllow will not disclose to third parties any personal information obtained from you, except as described in this Privacy Statement or when information was provided, or as provided for in the Terms &amp; Conditions.</p><h5>Personal Information</h5><p>SparkRebel is designed to enable you to connect to other people using their Facebook information. You may browse our Site without providing any personal information. However, the use of SparkRebel requires registration. When you register you will be asked to do so through Facebook Connect. In addition, in the course of using our Site, you may provide us with other personal information. Your personal information will be used primarily in connection with operating the Site, including contacting you so that we may provide the service you have requested or respond to your requests for information or customer service. This information may also be used to send you updates regarding our company or to share with you other services or benefits that may be of interest to you.</p><h5>Other Information We Collect</h5><p>PlumWIllow may collect certain information from visitors of the website, such as Internet addresses and other web log information (such as your web request, Internet Protocol (&ldquo;IP&rdquo;) address, browser type, browser language, referring / exit pages and URLs, platform type, number of clicks, domain names, landing pages, pages viewed and the order of those pages, the amount of time spent on particular pages, the date and time of your request, and one or more cookies that may uniquely identify your browser). This information is logged for internal use by PlumWillow, including helping diagnose technical problems and to administer our website in a manner that allows us to constantly improve the quality of the services provided to you. We may also maintain a record of your IP address, to analyze the use of our online services on an aggregate basis. We may also elect to share such information with advertisers and other third parties. PlumWillow is the sole owner of information collected on this Site. We reserve the right to screen, copy, transmit and review all communications conducted by or through the Site. We may conduct these activities for technical support purposes and in order to enforce our policies and agreements. We may decide to conduct these activities only at times or not at all.</p><h5>Cookies</h5><p>PlumWillow may use &ldquo;cookies&rdquo; to monitor visitors browsing our website. Cookies allow the server to store its own information about a user on the user&rsquo;s own computer. They can be used to customize pages for you based on information you may have provided to our website. Cookies may help us better serve you with information tailored specifically for you and for your return visit to our Site. Cookies are a typical part of web browsing today. Many websites that require you to type a password prior to entering a website use a cookie to facilitate the action. Additionally, many sites that do not require passwords also collect and utilize cookies. You are free to decline our cookies if your browser permits, although doing so may interfere with your use of the Site.</p><h5>Information Collected By Third Parties</h5><p>Our website may contain links to other websites. Those websites may be governed by terms and conditions and may have privacy policies that differ from ours. PlumWillow is not responsible for the privacy practices or the content of these other websites. You should exercise your discretion in disclosing personal information to other users of our Site. We are not responsible for any use of this information by others to whom you disclose such information by means of our Site. Third parties may improperly intercept or access transmissions or private communications, and other users may abuse or misuse your information that they collect from the Site. Therefore, although we try to protect your privacy, we cannot promise, and you should not expect, that your personal information or private communications will always remain encrypted and private. By using this Site, you agree to use all information collected in connection with this Site for legal purposes, only in connection with your permitted activities in connection with this Site or other purposes that the provider of such information has expressly chosen.</p><h5>Security</h5><p>The information you provide to us will be kept in our database. We will use reasonable means to protect the integrity and safety of the database. However, we cannot guarantee that the database will not be improperly accessed by third parties. PlumWillow uses a variety of multi-level security measures to protect you and our systems against unauthorized access to, or alteration, disclosure, destruction or loss of personal data hosted on our system. When an application or the Site is accessed through a web browser, Secure Socket Layer (SSL) or HTTPS technology will protect your information using both server authentication and data encryption. In this way, we try as hard as we can to ensure your data is secure, safe and accessible only by you.</p><h5>Password</h5><p>Your password is the key to your account. Use unique numbers, letters, and special characters and do not disclose your SparkRebel password to anyone. If you do share your password or your personal information with others, remember that you are responsible for all actions taken in the name of your account. If you lose control of your password, you may lose substantial control over your personal information and may be subject to legally binding actions taken on your behalf. Therefore, if your password has been compromised for any reason, you should immediately notify PlumWillow and change your password.</p><h5>Correcting &amp; Updating Your Information</h5><p>SparkRebel allows you to view the information you have provided after registration and to correct any inaccuracies or errors that may exist in the data.</p><h5>Our Disclosure of Your Information</h5><p>Your personal information may be disclosed to PlumWillow affiliates. In addition, we may disclose your personal information to third parties in connection with our operation of PlumWillow and the performing of the related services, including to service providers who help with our business operations. We may disclose your personal information to enforce our agreements and policies or respond to claims that information submitted or other content or Submissions violates applicable laws or regulations, the rights of others, or to protect anyone&rsquo;s rights, property, or safety. We also may disclose your information to respond to legal requirements or when we believe in good faith that the disclosure of information is necessary to prevent imminent harm or financial loss or to report suspected illegal activity. We may use our discretion to disclose your information under appropriate confidentiality conditions in connection with merger, acquisition or sale of asset or business activities involving our company or its affiliates. We may disclose non-personally identifying information (including, without limitation, aggregated information) as we believe is reasonable in connection with our business. This information will not identify individual users.</p><h5>Changes to the PlumWillow Privacy Policy</h5><p>PlumWillow reserves the right to amend this Privacy Policy from time to time by posting the amended terms on this Site.</p><h5>Additional Information</h5><p>If you have any questions or would like further information regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us.</p>"
